### Riders API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

# Update Online Status
PATCH {{baseURL}}/riders/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isOnline": true
}

###

# Update Location
PATCH {{baseURL}}/riders/location
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "latitude": 6.5244,
  "longitude": 3.3792
}

###

# Get My Deliveries
GET {{baseURL}}/riders/deliveries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}